articles.author: Joe Krishnan
articles.title: Chelsea may have made Moises Caicedo blunder after signing 'Brighton's replacement' - Express
articles.description: COMMENT: Chelsea could well have shot themselves in the foot in their pursuit of Moises Caicedo after clinching a deal to sign one of Brighton's potential replacements.
